Version 0.3.0
-------------
- replaced buildsystem automake with scons
- add API version to library name and install include files into a
  versioned subdirectory
- renamed include path from libgmbus to gmbus

Version 0.2.5
-------------
- Debian package support
- fixed bug with local interface

Version 0.2.4
-------------
- more IPv6 support
- patch with fixes for Mac OS X
- changed e-mail address

Version 0.2.3
-------------
- support option SEND_UNICAST to deactivate the optimation sending
  messages to unique receivers via unicast

Version 0.2.2
-------------
- closed memory leak
- fixed another bug for the mipsel architecture
- IPv6 support !!!
- new option INTERFACE in config file: select a specific network
  interface for unicats traffic

Version 0.2.1
-------------
- fixes for mipsel architecture (works on linksys router)
  printf length modifier 'll' does not work

Version 0.2.0
-------------
- new memory management
- some small API changes
- a bunch of bug fixes
- Mbus integers are 64 bit numbers
- scope HOSTLOCAL fixes
- new method for calculating RPC ids
